c', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/187774/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767365209);
